{"tid":1229154,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【陳雲】我給Carrie 姐顯示香港是主權國的能力","createTime":"2019-06-15T23:11:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-16T08:31:23.000Z","uid":259321,"like":658,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":55,"replies":[{"pid":"968b2bee00b20f35deb775fe467798818d0fbef4","tid":1229154,"uid":259321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T23:11:58.000Z","msg":"陳雲：我給Carrie 姐顯示香港是主權國的能力。習近平無論如何，是不可能將Carrie辭退的。<br />\n即使到了任滿，只要Carrie停止展開選舉特首的程序，她就是香港的永久特首。法律上，中共對她毫無辦法，因為香港是主權國。<br />\n我以前講過，如果中共元首到香港來，特首下令警察將他射殺，中國也只能發出外交照會，也無法引渡特首回北京受審。即使修了逃犯引渡條例也無法引渡，因為引渡令是要特首簽署同意的。<br />\nCarrie，頂住，而且在本屆任滿之後不啟動特首選舉，你就是終身特首，看中共奈你什麼何。<br />\n我回來了。幫Carrie 收驚、壯膽。武則天，頂住。"},{"pid":"a5d8c298b8dc5afa00e548625a035fa08d4fa3b6","tid":1229154,"uid":82938,"like":20,"dislike":3,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T23:12:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71fc1b59ddf6b3dd1035a152c324a36ef170ace6","tid":1229154,"uid":237562,"like":67,"dislike":0,"score":67,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T23:14:04.000Z","msg":"刺殺習近平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e9436d962a0fe55bbd671878d962cbe3d4ddfbe","tid":1229154,"uid":259321,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T23:19:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fe0d984ca9895b77f9c7431c5a6c6c1704891190","tid":1229154,"uid":76591,"like":281,"dislike":3,"score":278,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T23:21:19.000Z","msg":"國師其實真係勁<br />\n不過有D野講早咗<br />\n例如永續基本法<br />\n家陣大家應該明係乜野意思了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c717647e9d48eea218e29b6bc0b753234509206","tid":1229154,"uid":171273,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T23:24:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b1521e3c7ca3ad02d056e3908990b271eb60867","tid":1229154,"uid":159913,"