能將Carrie辭退的。<br />\n即使到了任滿，只要Carrie停止展開選舉特首的程序，她就是香港的永久特首。法律上，中共對她毫無辦法，因為香港是主權國。<br />\n我以前講過，如果中共元首到香港來，特首下令警察將他射殺，中國也只能發出外交照會，也無法引渡特首回北京受審。即使修了逃犯引渡條例也無法引渡，因為引渡令是要特首簽署同意的。<br />\nCarrie，頂住，而且在本屆任滿之後不啟動特首選舉，你就是終身特首，看中共奈你什麼何。<br />\n我回來了。幫Carrie 收驚、壯膽。武則天，頂住。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T00:40:02.000Z","msg":"樓主小心又俾泛民左膠打手屈你係熱狗，甚至更過份屈你係三毛五毛"},{"pid":"d581ede60636224393634cb3e43589d33216dbd8","tid":1229154,"uid":225347,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T00:42:42.000Z","msg":"港獨之母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"214603b40513f4efd81b3cb1696f95924bcb525a","tid":1229154,"uid":28435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T00:43:13.000Z","msg":"國師又中 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"168bf30234d7d66b49b7f1b594c321a9fb884180","tid":1229154,"uid":186152,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T00:54:13.000Z","msg":"港獨之母林奠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f616a8a686013543dcfcb1611f5d40ff1400b433","tid":1229154,"uid":188721,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T00:55:06.000Z","msg":"國師係真正嘅預言家！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98d351f6d3c4e7bea31e79e91d35616696104f36","tid":1229154,"uid":188721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T00:56:36.000Z","msg":"推推佢"},{"pid":"550797201327bd71deb78b8c188f1d9b5c77f002","tid":1229154,"uid":259321,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"bbf8a4e0644dd2191b8117afc9196b3ac1f153d7","tid":1229154,"uid":241151,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"968b2bee00b20f35deb775fe467798818d0fbef4","tid":1229154,"uid":259321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T23:11:58.000Z"