 />\n但佢話係香港整死中國元首<br />\n解放軍即刻出場啦<br />\n(又或者趁大陸內亂宣布獨立)"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T02:38:15.000Z","msg":"一國兩制在歷史上發生過100萬次，結果不是改土歸流，就是自治政府趁着中央管治薄弱時，宣布獨立。這是永遠改變不了的政治現實。<br />\n<br />\n這條例不過是進一步的「一國一制化」罷了，而這早在1984年，已經肯定了有今日的情况了。大家如果以為「一國兩制」可以奉行至2047年才一夕大變，是不可能的，這並不符合歷史規律。"},{"pid":"0dac410c6e1899152f2a0fc03b95cff76f0cbce0","tid":1229154,"uid":93043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T02:45:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cf1627f33ff6375352ecb3d9efd1c4362eb60efc","tid":1229154,"uid":82640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0dac410c6e1899152f2a0fc03b95cff76f0cbce0","tid":1229154,"uid":93043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"19cbaf3042f0952f6b574c8a75e96bf5b71d51e4","tid":1229154,"uid":82640,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"2771342a8218bff0815ff0ab906fbe320c075234","tid":1229154,"uid":93043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T02:12:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T02:16:21.000Z","msg":"要特首出憲報宣布選舉日子<br />\n其實特首有可能唔小心唔記得解散區議會、立法會，特首選舉日子唔公佈...<br />\n<br />\n當然點會玩撚到咁大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T02:45:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T02:47:11.000Z","msg":"行政長官可停止律政司司長職務<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d38c27340845563a71a9a95df01ec9b3ae7e983","tid":1229154,"uid":2607,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T02:47:13.000Z","msg":"玩膠世界第一<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />不過睇返之前幾篇都幾正<br />\n利申unlike左好耐"},{"pid":"ed919a4e7fa12fe420ecc0d403f8826c7262bfa3","tid":1229154,"uid":155246,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"0dac410c6e1899152f2a0fc03b95cff76f0cbce0","tid":1229154,"uid":93043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"19cbaf3042f0952f6b574c8a75e96bf5b71d51e4","tid":1229154,"uid":82640,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quo